  <data name="Winget_Description" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Software na rubutu kan hoton allo don Windows da Linux.

Fasaloli:
- **Kibiyoyi** - Jan hankali zuwa wurare na musamman da kibiyoyi masu saukaka
- **Bayani** - Ƙara bayanin kumfa mai iya gyarawa
- **Rubutu** - Ƙirƙiri akwatunan rubutu don ƙarin bayani
- **Zaɓin Iyaka** - Nuna wurare tare da murabba'i masu iyaka
- **Ruɓa** - Ɓoye bayani mai mahimmanci da tasirin ruɓa
- **Kayan aikin Zaɓi** - Zaɓi sassa na hoto don kwafi (Ctrl+C) ko gogewa (maɓallin Delete)
- **Yanke sassan tsaye da kwance** - Yanke sassan tsaye ko kwance na hoto
- **Haskaka** - Haskaka wurare masu sha'awa
- **Sarrafa Ayyuka** - Adana aiki ta atomatik da ƙananan hoto na duba
- **Ƙetare dandali** - Yana aiki a Windows da Linux duka</value>
  </data>
